contentrichtext.text: '''Hancock''' may refer to: {{TOCright}} ==People== *See [[Hancock (surname)]] ==Places== In the United States: *[[Hancock, Iowa]] *[[Hancock, Maine]] *[[Hancock, Maryland]] *[[Hancock, Massachusetts]] *[[Hancock, Michigan]] *[[Hancock, Minnesota]] *[[Hancock, New Hampshire]] *[[Hancock (town), New York]] **[[Hancock (village), New York]], in the town of Hancock *[[Hancock, Austin, Texas]], a neighborhood in [[Austin, Texas|Austin]], [[Texas]] *[[Hancock, Vermont]] *[[Hancock (town), Wisconsin]] **[[Hancock, Wisconsin]], a village within the town *[[Hancock Township, Michigan]] *[[Hancock Township, Carver County, Minnesota]] ==Entertainment== * [[Hancock (film)|''Hancock'' (film)]], a 2008 superhero film starring Will Smith * [[List of One Piece characters#Boa Hancock|Boa Hancock]], a character in the ''One Piece'' manga and anime series * ''[[Hancock's Half Hour]]'', a British radio and TV comedy programme, eventually shortened to ''Hancock'' ==Other uses== * [[Hancock air whistle]], a whistle intended for use on diesel locomotives * [[Hancock Museum]], a natural history museum in Newcastle upon Tyne, England * [[John Hancock Insurance]], a US company * [[John Hancock Tower]], a building in Boston, Massachusetts, owned by the insurance firm * [[USS Hancock|USS ''Hancock'']], the name of several ships belonging to the United States Navy ==See also== * [[Hancock County (disambiguation)]], a list of counties in several US states * [[Mount Hancock (disambiguation)]] {{disambiguation}} [[Category:Place name disambiguation pages]]
